sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Biz as 业务线程（@LogCollect 方法）
    participant Aspect as LogCollectAspect（AOP）
    participant PM as LogCollectPipelineManager
    participant App as LogCollectAppender（Logback/Log4j2）
    participant Ring as PipelineRingBuffer
    participant Consumer as PipelineConsumer 线程
    participant Buffer as SingleWriterBuffer / AggregateDirectBuffer
    participant Flush as AsyncFlushExecutor（logcollect-flush-*）
    participant Retry as ResilientFlusher（retry-scheduler）
    participant Handler as LogCollectHandler
    participant Degrade as DegradeFallbackHandler（FILE/MEMORY）

    Note over Biz,PM: 默认主路径：pipeline.enabled=true && useBuffer=true
    Biz->>Aspect: 进入 @LogCollect 方法
    Aspect->>Aspect: resolve config/handler/circuitBreaker
    Aspect->>PM: registerContext(ctx)
    PM->>Ring: new PipelineRingBuffer(ring, overflow)
    PM->>Consumer: assign(ctx)
    Aspect->>Handler: before(ctx)

    loop 业务方法内 log.xxx()
        Biz->>App: append(event)
        App->>App: traceId匹配 + 级别/Logger过滤
        alt Pipeline 打开且队列是 RingBuffer
            App->>Ring: tryClaim()
            alt claim 成功
                App->>Ring: getSlot().populate(...)
                App->>Ring: publish(sequence)
            else claim 失败
                alt WARN 及以上
                    App->>Ring: offerOverflow(raw)
                    alt overflow 满
                        App->>Degrade: handleDegraded(PIPELINE_QUEUE_FULL)
                    end
                else 低等级
                    App->>App: backpressure discard + metrics
                end
            end
        else Pipeline 关闭（兼容分支）
            alt useBuffer=true
                App->>Buffer: offer(...)（SingleMode/AggregateMode）
                alt async=true 且阈值触发
                    Buffer->>Flush: submit AsyncBufferFlushTask
                    Flush->>Handler: appendLog / flushAggregatedLog
                end
            else useBuffer=false
                alt async=true
                    App->>Flush: submit writeTask
                    Flush->>Handler: appendLog / flushAggregatedLog
                else async=false
                    App->>Handler: 业务线程直接写入
                end
            end
        end
    end

    loop Consumer 轮询 assignedContexts
        Consumer->>Ring: pollOverflow() / tryConsume()
        alt 有记录
            Consumer->>Consumer: shouldCollect + SecurityPipeline
            alt SINGLE
                Consumer->>Buffer: SingleWriterBuffer.offer(LogEntry)
                alt 达阈值
                    Consumer->>Handler: 批量 appendLog（ResilientFlusher）
                end
            else AGGREGATE
                Consumer->>Buffer: AggregateDirectBuffer.append(record)
                alt 达阈值
                    Consumer->>Handler: flushAggregatedLog（ResilientFlusher）
                end
            end
            alt flush 重试耗尽
                Consumer->>Retry: backoff retry
                Retry->>Degrade: 持久化失败降级（FILE/MEMORY）
            end
        else 空闲
            Consumer->>Consumer: idle(PARK/YIELD/SPIN)
        end
    end

    Biz->>Aspect: 方法结束（return/throw）
    Aspect->>PM: closeContext(ctx)
    PM->>Consumer: closeAndFlush(ctx, handoffTimeout)
    Consumer->>Ring: drain 到 producerCursor（超时 slot 会 skip+discard）
    Consumer->>Buffer: final flush（SINGLE/AGGREGATE）
    Consumer-->>PM: countDown close latch + markClosed
    Aspect->>Handler: after(ctx)
    Aspect->>Aspect: LogCollectContextManager.pop() + MDC 清理
